title: 'Overall Good'
body: Only mattress with stand, overall nice concept and quality, however though top material is made of thick textile, can get damaged during transit (see photo), but nothing a little stitching won't fix. The pillows were soft, but the sofa itself not very soft, just pliable. Color was as shown, as was size. Overall recommended.
